name: Art Title 2
description: Since becoming an international champion, RoxRite hadn't battled at home in the Bay in four years. Adding to that, crew tension was in the air; there had been a vote to send Victor instead of Nasty Ray to an earlier competition. "We were thinking for the crew", explained RoxRite, "and the name, and if we take Victor, we have a better chance of winning because Ray hadn’t been on point, but Ray didn’t take it well. Of course that’s understandable. So I was just like 'let’s battle'". Ray and RoxRite would rep the Squadron for this hometown competition. "He’s still my friend outside of whatever situation happens." "We killed it", RoxRite said, and bringing the situation full circle, the pair battled Victor in the final. "That’s what I think our relationship is", says Nasty Ray. "Straightforward, honest. 'What’s bugging you?' We’re just very straightforward about it." (December 2014)
